Road closures will be implemented as precincts and car parks reach capacity in the Royal National Park.

If parking capacity is reached across all precincts, traffic will only be permitted to travel through the park. Entry will be maintained via McKell Ave at Waterfall for residents only.

Visitors are encouraged to check the Royal National Park local alerts before travelling for updates on precinct access.

  • Maianbar Rd between Bundeena Dr and Maianbar township
